Package: FARS
Type: Package
Title: FARS data analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lawrence Cox
Maintainer: Lawrence Cox <lawrencecox@hotmail.co.uk>
Description: This package has functions which will read a fars csv 
    file based on an input of a list of years, which will provide a 
    dataframe from which a summary of accidents for a given year and
    month can be obtained, and which plots accidents on a map of US 
    states based on inputs of a year and a state.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: readr,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    graphics,
    stats,
    magrittr,
    maps
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
